      "title": "Inicio",
      "slug": "home",
      "content": [
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<section id=\"about-us-section\" class=\"about-us-section\">" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<h2>Entrena a tu aire</h2>" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<p>En <strong>DeloxFit</strong> no te vamos a vender la moto. Esto es un gimnasio para gente normal que solo quiere entrenar tranquila y sin tonterías.</p>" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<p>Da igual si es tu primer día. Aquí nadie te va a mirar raro. Abrimos <strong>las 24 horas</strong> para que vengas cuando te dé la gana.</p>" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<strong>Calle del Esfuerzo, 42, Planta 1, 35021 Las Palmas</strong>" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<img src=\"./assets/about-us.png\" alt=\"DeloxFit\"></section>" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<section id=\"facilities-section\" class=\"facilities-section\"><h2>INSTALACIONES</h2>" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<div class=\"carousel-container\"><div class=\"carousel-slide\">" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<img src=\"./assets/carousel/c5.png\"><img src=\"./assets/carousel/c4.png\"><img src=\"./assets/carousel/c3.png\">" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "</div></div></section>" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<section id=\"classes-banner-section\" class=\"classes-banner-section\" data-xlu-include-file=\"./templates/banner.html\" data-title=\"CLASES\" data-image=\"./assets/classes-banner.jpg\" data-link=\"./classesPage.html\"></section>" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<section id=\"subscriptions-banner-section\" class=\"subscriptions-banner-section\" data-xlu-include-file=\"./templates/banner.html\" data-title=\"SUSCRIPCIONES\" data-image=\"./assets/subscription-banner.png\" data-link=\"./subscriptionPage.html\"></section>" } ] }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Aviso Legal",
      "slug": "legal",
      "content": [
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<h1 id=\"legal-title\">AVISO LEGAL</h1>" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<section id=\"identification-section\"><h2>1. DATOS IDENTIFICATIVOS</h2>" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<p>En cumplimiento con el deber de información, se facilitan los siguientes datos:</p>" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<ul><li><strong>Nombre Comercial:</strong> DeloxFit</li><li><strong>Titular:</strong> Andrés Barroso Soriano</li><li><strong>NIF/CIF:</strong> B-76543210</li><li><strong>Dirección:</strong> Calle del Esfuerzo, 42, Planta 1, 35021 Las Palmas</li><li><strong>Email de Contacto:</strong> contacto@deloxfit.com</li></ul></section>" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<section id=\"acceptance-section\"><h2>2. USUARIOS Y ACEPTACIÓN</h2>" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<p>El acceso y/o uso de este portal de <strong>DeloxFit</strong> le atribuye la condición de <strong>USUARIO</strong>.</p></section>" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<section id=\"portal-usage-section\"><h2>3. USO DEL PORTAL</h2><p>El sitio web de DeloxFit proporciona el acceso a multitud de informaciones.</p></section>" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<section id=\"privacy-section\"><h2>4. PROTECCIÓN DE DATOS (RGPD)</h2><p>DeloxFit cumple con las directrices del Reglamento General de Protección de Datos (RGPD).</p></section>" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<section id=\"property-section\"><h2>5. PROPIEDAD INTELECTUAL E INDUSTRIAL</h2><p>DeloxFit es titular de todos los derechos de propiedad intelectual e industrial.</p></section>" } ] },
        { "type": "paragraph", "children": [ { "type": "text", "text": "<section id=\"liability-section\"><h2>6. EXCLUSIÓN DE RESPONSABILIDAD</h2><p>DeloxFit no se hace responsable de los daños y perjuicios.</p></section>" } ] }
      ]
    },
